      • divideRectRecursive

        private void divideRectRecursive(javafx.scene.shape.Rectangle rect,
                                 java.util.List<javafx.scene.shape.Line> lineList)
        Breaks a rectangle down into a list of line segments by subdividing the rectangle until all resulting rectangles are under a defined width of approx. 3.78 pixels. Then the midpoint of each rectangle is used to create a line segment.
        Parameters:
        rect - Rectangle
        lineList - List<Line>
